VALUES ('202005', 'Geometric Pattern Bangle with Crystal Accents - Artificial Rose Gold', 'This stylish bangle, crafted in artificial rose gold, features a modern design with distinct geometric shapes. A black and gold diamond-shaped charm with a central motif is juxtaposed with a larger, openwork diamond filled with sparkling clear crystals. A smaller, kite-like accent further embellishes the band, which is also lined with delicate crystals. The bracelet is presented on a textured marble surface, highlighting its contemporary and elegant appeal.Size: Free Size upto 2.6 Size.Free shipping on orders over ?498/- Happy shopping!', 499, 999, 'bracelet', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/483/image_128?unique=1744736580000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/483/image_128?unique=1744736580000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/32/image_1920?unique=1744736580000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/33/image_1920?unique=1744736580000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0202005-geometric-pattern-bangle-with-crystal-accents-artificial-rose-gold-483', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
