VALUES ('701017', 'Marquise Red Stone and Cubic Zirconia Halo Ring - Artificial Yellow Gold', 'This elegant ring features a vibrant marquise-cut artificial ruby as its center stone, showcasing a rich red hue. The ruby is surrounded by a delicate halo of sparkling clear cubic zirconia stones, enhancing its brilliance. The band is crafted in artificial yellow gold and is also adorned with small, pave-set clear cubic zirconia stones along its shoulders, adding further sparkle. The ring is presented on a smooth, white stone, which rests on a luxurious marble surface with subtle veining, highlighting its classic design and vibrant gemstone.Free shipping on orders over ?498/- Happy shopping!', 249, 499, 'rings', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/548/image_128?unique=1746028713000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/548/image_128?unique=1746028713000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/258/image_1920?unique=1745332009000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/259/image_1920?unique=1745332009000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0701017-marquise-red-stone-and-cubic-zirconia-halo-ring-artificial-yellow-gold-548', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
