VALUES ('702002', 'Cushion Cut Champagne Cubic Zirconia Halo Ring with Pave Band - Artificial Rose Gold', 'This exquisite engagement ring features a beautiful cushion-cut morganite as its center stone, displaying a delicate peach hue. It is surrounded by a halo of sparkling clear diamonds, enhancing its soft color and brilliance. The band is crafted in 18k rose gold and is also adorned with pave-set diamonds, adding a continuous sparkle. The ring is elegantly presented on a smooth, white stone, which rests on a luxurious marble surface with subtle veining, highlighting its romantic and sophisticated design. Free shipping on orders over â?498/- Happy shopping!', 249, 499, 'rings', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/533/image_128?unique=1759160921000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/533/image_128?unique=1759160921000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/195/image_1920?unique=1745324731000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/196/image_1920?unique=1745324731000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0702002-cushion-cut-champagne-cubic-zirconia-halo-ring-with-pave-band-artificial-rose-gold-533', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
