VALUES ('801004', 'Pear-Shaped Crystal Pendant and Earrings Set - Artificial Yellow Gold', 'This elegant jewelry set features a matching pendant necklace and drop earrings, all crafted in artificial yellow gold. The pendant showcases a stylized pear shape with an intricate openwork design and is outlined with sparkling clear crystals. A larger pear-shaped clear crystal is set at the top, and a smaller, crystal-encrusted pear-shaped charm dangles below. The matching drop earrings mirror the design of the lower part of the pendant, featuring a pear-shaped clear crystal surrounded by smaller crystals.', 699, 1499, 'pendant_sets', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/529/image_128?unique=1758960265000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/529/image_128?unique=1758960265000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/183/image_1920?unique=1745320675000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0801004-pear-shaped-crystal-pendant-and-earrings-set-artificial-yellow-gold-529', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
