VALUES ('801005', 'Concentric Circle Crystal Pendant and Earrings Set - Artificial Yellow Gold', 'This elegant jewelry set features a matching pendant necklace and stud earrings, all with a concentric circle design and a gold-tone finish. The pendant is larger and features multiple rings of sparkling clear crystals emanating from a central, darker stone. The outer edge of the pendant has a detailed, geometric openwork design. The matching stud earrings mirror the central concentric crystal design of the pendant. The set is presented on a textured white surface, highlighting the intricate details and sparkling crystals against the warm gold tone.', 699, 1499, 'pendant_sets', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/530/image_128?unique=1745322245000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/530/image_128?unique=1745322245000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/185/image_1920?unique=1745322177000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0801005-concentric-circle-crystal-pendant-and-earrings-set-artificial-yellow-gold-530', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
