VALUES ('802001', 'Enameled Butterfly Pendant and Earrings Set - Artificial Rose Gold', 'This charming jewelry set features a delicate pendant necklace and matching stud earrings, all crafted in artificial rose gold. The pendant showcases a stylized teardrop shape with two enameled butterflies in shades of blue and teal, accented with small clear crystals. The teardrop outline is also partially embellished with sparkling crystals. The matching stud earrings feature individual enameled butterflies in the same vibrant blue and teal, each with a crystal accent. The set is presented on a textured white surface, highlighting the intricate details and vibrant colors of the butterflies against the warm rose gold tone.Free shipping on orders over ?498/- Happy shopping!', 699, 1499, 'pendant_sets', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/526/image_128?unique=1745829655000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/526/image_128?unique=1745829655000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/176/image_1920?unique=1745320032000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0802001-enameled-butterfly-pendant-and-earrings-set-artificial-rose-gold-526', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
