VALUES ('802003', 'Enameled Butterfly Charms with Crystal Accents - Artificial Yellow Gold', 'Each butterfly features intricate blue and teal enamel detailing, outlining the wings and body. The upper wings of each butterfly are adorned with small, sparkling clear crystals along the edges, adding a touch of glamour. The largest butterfly at the bottom also has additional small crystals in teal and clear along its body. Each charm has small loops for attaching to jewelry findings. They are displayed on a textured white surface, highlighting their vibrant colors and sparkling accents.', 699, 1499, 'pendant_sets', 50, 'https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/528/image_128?unique=1758956127000', '["https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.template/528/image_128?unique=1758956127000","https://www.kaapav.com/web/image/product.image/365/image_1920?unique=1758956092000"]', 1, 0, 1, '[]', 'https://www.kaapav.com/shop/0802003-enameled-butterfly-charms-with-crystal-accents-artificial-yellow-gold-528', 'Anti-Tarnish Artificial Jewellery');
